@startuml Seq-05 Check Out

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 5
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

actor       "Driver"            as Driver
participant "API Gateway"       as GW
participant "Presence Service"  as Presence
participant "Billing Service"   as Billing
participant "Payment Service"   as Payment
participant "Payment Gateway"   as PGW
database    "PostgreSQL"        as DB

note over Driver : Driver finishes parking\nand taps "Check Out" in app

Driver -> GW : POST /sessions/checkout\n{ session_id, driver_id }
GW -> Presence : CheckOut(session_id, driver_id)

Presence -> DB : SELECT * FROM sessions WHERE id=session_id
DB --> Presence : session (ACTIVE, checked_in_at)

Presence -> DB : UPDATE sessions\nSET status=COMPLETED,\n    checked_out_at=now()
DB --> Presence : OK

Presence -> DB : UPDATE spots SET status=AVAILABLE\nWHERE id=spot_id
DB --> Presence : OK (spot released immediately)

Presence -> DB : UPDATE reservations\nSET status=COMPLETED
DB --> Presence : OK

Presence -> Billing : CalculateAndCreateInvoice(\n  idempotency_key, session_id,\n  checked_in_at, checked_out_at)

Billing -> Billing : PricingEngine.Calculate()\n→ hours=ceil(duration/60)\n→ parking_fee=hours×5000\n→ overnight_fee=20000 if crosses midnight

Billing -> DB : INSERT INTO invoices\n(status=PENDING_PAYMENT,\n parking_fee, overnight_fee, total, ...)
DB --> Billing : invoice_id

Billing -> Payment : CreatePayment(\n  idempotency_key,\n  reference_id=invoice_id,\n  type=PARKING_FEE,\n  amount=parking_fee+overnight_fee)
Payment -> DB : INSERT INTO payments\n(status=PENDING, ...)
DB --> Payment : payment_id
Payment -> PGW : Create QRIS payment
PGW --> Payment : qr_code_url
Payment --> Billing : { payment_id, qr_code_url }

Billing --> Presence : CreateInvoiceResponse\n{ invoice_id, total_idr, qr_code_url }
Presence --> GW : CheckOutResponse\n{ session_id, invoice_id,\n  total_idr, qr_code_url }
GW --> Driver : 200 OK { invoice_id, total_idr, qr_code_url }

note over Driver : Driver scans QRIS and pays.\nSee Seq-07 for payment outcome.

@enduml
